On 4 June 2012, modern PET/CT scanner was officially opened at University Hospital--report from the opening ceremony Krakow (Poland). On the 4th of June, the PET/CT center has been opened in Cracow. That hybrid system has been installed in Nuclear Medicine Center which is part of Endocrinology Department of University Hospital. This is one of the sixteen PET/CT scanners operate in whole Poland and first public hybrid equipment in province of Malopolska.